-----------------------------------------------------------
Description:

vmbd_chimney.py    Test script for online multiframe 
                   blind deconvolution on chimney sequence
olaGPU.py          Library for spatially-varying convolution
		   incl. various deconvolution algorithms
imagetools.py      Some image processing functions 
gputools.py        Wrapping functions of Cuda code
*.cu               Cuda code

-----------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies:

This library requires PyCuda (tested with version 
2011.1.2 and version 0.94.2) as well as the pyfft 
package (tested with version 0.3.5). See Andreas 
Kloeckner's project homepage
    
http://mathema.tician.de/software/pycuda
    
for details on PyCuda and its dependencies, as well as

http://pypi.python.org/pypi/pyfft.

for the installation guide of pyfft.

